11. ONE-LINE FINAL REVISION
=========================================

- vector = fastest traversal
- list = fastest middle insertion
- deque = both ends fast
- map = sorted key-value
- unordered_map = fastest lookup
- set = sorted unique
- stack = LIFO
- queue = FIFO
- priority_queue = heap (top element access)

